'''敲桌事件'''，亦称'''[[尼基塔·赫鲁晓夫|尼基塔·赫鲁晓夫]]的敲桌事件'''，发生在1960年10月12日的[[联合国大会|联合国大会]]第902次会议期间。

有观点认为时任[[苏共中央主要负责人列表|苏联共产党中央委员会第一书记]]的[[赫鲁晓夫|赫鲁晓夫]]之所以敲鞋是因为[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]代表[[洛伦佐·萨姆朗|洛伦佐·萨姆朗]]在他演说时反驳及抨击苏联在[[东欧|东欧]]幹的正是他们所反对的[[殖民主义|殖民主义]]，并指责苏联虚伪，激怒了赫鲁晓夫。有观点认为赫鲁晓夫是在[[英国首相|英国首相]][[哈羅德·麥美倫|哈羅德·麥美倫]]发表同样指责他的言论后才拿鞋敲桌的。<ref name="macmillan khrushchev&f=false">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=bxtPWOIlx9sC&pg=PA230&lpg=PA230&dq=shoe+macmillan+khrushchev&source=bl&ots=u6NAtTubo-&sig=L3V2d0evMVlVvp2-B0MeR6qenPY&hl=ru&sa=X&ei=IaFbUOPpFvHR4QTJ7IHQAg&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=shoe%20macmillan%20khrushchev&f=false|title=Khrushchev: A Political Life|author=William J. Tompson|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|year=1997|isbn=978-0312163600}}</ref><ref name="books.google.com">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XIwepaauUaQC&pg=PA172&lpg=PA172&dq=shoe+macmillan+khrushchev&source=bl&ots=rhrQu8jLgR&sig=-huOUEke_2aMQgRyA-2VzvJOL88&hl=ru&sa=X&ei=u6FbUKvyOvL34QTurYGACw&ved=0CFQQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=shoe%20macmillan%20khrushchev&f=false|title=On This Day: Volume One|author=David Phillips|publisher=iUniverse|year=2007|isbn=978-0595462889|page=172}}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=yUD8D-UynoYC&pg=PA150&lpg=PA150&dq=shoe+macmillan+khrushchev&source=bl&ots=TUTAFRUCIb&sig=4awJvQOH_WL72jcVKExQP-8v8KU&hl=ru&sa=X&ei=u6FbUKvyOvL34QTurYGACw&ved=0CD4Q6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=shoe%20macmillan%20khrushchev&f=false|title=Eisenhower, Macmillan and Allied Unity 1957-61|author=E. Bruce Geelhoed|author2=Anthony O. Edmonds|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|year=2003|isbn=978-0333642276}}</ref>也有說法是赫鲁晓夫當時只有揮舞鞋子，並非拿鞋敲桌。

尽管各方都认为赫鲁晓夫被萨姆朗和麦美伦的讲话激怒了，并大声斥责他们，但是却没有留存的摄影录像可以佐证。<ref name="NY Times 2003">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/07/26/opinion/26iht-edtaubman_ed3_.html|title=Did he bang it?: Nikita Khrushchev and the shoe|author=William Taubman|date=2003-07-26|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2010-09-28|archive-date=2012-06-08|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68H0uKXKX?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/07/26/opinion/26iht-edtaubman_ed3_.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>廣泛流傳的赫鲁晓夫挥舞鞋子的照片其實是假造的，是在赫鲁晓夫挥舞的空手上後製加入鞋子的影像。<ref>{{cite web |author=Fred Bals |title=K Blows Top! |publisher=Dreamtime |date=July 15, 2009 |url=http://www.dreamtimepodcast.com/2009/07/k-blows-top.html |access-date=2015-06-16 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204203043/http://www.dreamtimepodcast.com/2009/07/k-blows-top.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

